OL,5, The boss of the UK's third largest     
OL,6, energy supplier has proposed a plan for
OL,7, the government to subsidise soaring    
OL,8, bills for the poorest households.      
OL,10,FSteven Fitzpatrick, founder of Ovo     
OL,11,FEnergy, wants the help to taper off for
OL,12,Fhigh earners who use more electricity. 
OL,14,FHe said a plan was needed now before   
OL,15,Fthe winter, otherwise the poorest      
OL,16,Fhouseholds would be cold and hungry.   
OL,18,FThe government said it was preparing to
OL,19,Fdeliver any extra support as soon as a 
OL,20,Fnew prime minister is in place.        
